if (file.exists("alcohol.rds")) {
  data <- readRDS("alcohol.rds")
} else {
  url <- "https://xdaiisu.github.io/ds202materials/data/ames.csv"
  data <- readr::read_csv(url)
  saveRDS(data, file="alcohol.rds")
}
